    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "地方"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（地方上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "地方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哽哼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "地方",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "地方地方，差事难当。一卯不到，两腿遭殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "地方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，赵州桥地方是也。今有包大人，陈州放粮而回，打此经过，不免前去伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": "地方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就此走走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "地方",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打道前来，打道前来，四方人站开。闲人让路，坐地把身抬，坐地把身抬！"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.0,
        0.2,
        0.6,
        0.2,
        0.0,
        1,
        0.0,
        0.0
      ]
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李后"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李后上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想当年在皇宫何等幸侥，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我一朝正国母作了贫民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "五谷丰登有收成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身李后。只因癸未年间，身怀六甲。宫中有一刘妃，与内侍郭槐，定下一计。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在老王面前，讨下收生代劳旨意。将金丝狸猫剥去皮尾，换去太子，奏与老"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王，道哀家生产妖魔鬼怪。老王大怒，将哀家推出午门问斩。多亏满朝文武保"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奏，死罪以免，活罪难饶，将哀家打入冷宫。他二人一计不成，又生一计，约"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "定八月十五火焚冷宫。只见火光一起，也不知那位神圣，将哀家救在这破瓦寒"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窑来了。天哪，天哪！这二十载的冤仇，何日得报吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "儿在朝中多倖僧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "娘在寒窑受苦情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我好比这萍草无根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，列位，哪里这样热闹？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众人 （内同白） 包大人陈州放粮而回，打此经过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦呵唉呀，原来是包拯陈州放粮而回，打此经过。我不免赶上前去，将我二十"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在的冤仇，对他伸诉便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李后",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说来了包文正，二十载的冤仇要伸明！"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "内白": 1,
          "stage_direction": 6,
          "唱": 1,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.333,
        "dominant_style_family": "二黄",
        "musical_styles": [
          "二黄原板",
          "二黄慢板",
          "二黄摇板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        0.333,
